7
00:00:37,930 --> 00:00:41,800
I look cute!

8
00:00:46,780 --> 00:00:50,050
<i>That incident was reported
in the newspapers.</i>

9
00:00:50,050 --> 00:00:52,810
<i>So we were getting
carried away by it.</i>

10
00:01:03,230 --> 00:01:06,360
The customers have been
looking at us all week!

11
00:01:19,980 --> 00:01:21,610
She's cute.

12
00:01:26,080 --> 00:01:28,680
- Enjoy!
- You're getting carried away.

13
00:01:28,680 --> 00:01:30,490
Can you tell?

14
00:01:32,890 --> 00:01:35,420
- Isn't it strange?
- It sure is.

15
00:01:36,220 --> 00:01:40,600
Why doesn't the doctor
get any credit for it?

16
00:01:41,030 --> 00:01:43,570
- Didn't I help, too?
- So did I.

17
00:01:43,570 --> 00:01:47,170
They didn't do anything, but
they get all the attention.

18
00:01:47,740 --> 00:01:49,340
This is truly upsetting.

19
00:01:50,070 --> 00:01:51,540
Let's go.

20
00:01:55,110 --> 00:01:58,950
Thank you for coming
to our pub today.

21
00:02:02,050 --> 00:02:04,550
All kinds of things
happen during the summer.

22
00:02:04,550 --> 00:02:06,190
When you want a case solved,

23
