come to Kirishima Detective
Office on the third floor.

24
00:02:11,960 --> 00:02:14,400
For your summer colds,
come and see the very

25
00:02:14,400 --> 00:02:17,170
beautiful Dr. Asami.

26
00:02:23,710 --> 00:02:26,070
Don't forget what I just said.

27
